I can only move my knight back.  If I try to bolster with Be3, the best I can hope for is an even exchange (bad for me if I want to exploit his pawn structure) and the worst is my queen getting forked.  On average, I lose a pawn and give him control of the f-file.
He gives me an opening to the kingside, and he misreads my setup move as preparation to attach the c4 pawn.  His bishop is now neatly tucked away on the side of the board and completely useless.
